title: Harderstyles Torrentz Presents: New Releases Pack September 2016
description:
=====================================
=======Harderstyles Torrentz=========
==============Presents===============
=====New Releases September 2016=====
=====================================
 
- This month a New Record is Set with 272 Tracks in this Pack!!!.
  This was a extremely good month for me getting new releases for ya'll.
  For the Hardcore Lovers there is suprisingly alot of hardcore releases in this pack.
  Hope you all enjoy this release!! <-HTorr3ntz
- Sorry for the late release!! - this pack took me longer due to private reasons.
  Hope ya'all can forgive me for that <3

Message From HTorr3ntz:
===================================
- Please leave a Comment.
- Please keep seeding.
